-- Rupert Murdoch meets Italian PM in Rome
-- 
-- Thu Jun 28, 2007 5:57am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/06/28/us-italy-murdoch-idUSL2834757520070628

 

 ROME  (Reuters) - Media mogul Rupert Murdoch, who heads news and broadcasting group News Corp., met Italian Prime Minister Romano Prodi on Thursday. 

 No further details were available on the meeting. Murdoch, whose media expire includes Italian television channel Sky Italia, has said he had discussed taking a stake in leading Italian telecoms group Telecom Italia last year but decided against it.